    <item>
      <title>ColddBox - Walkthrough</title>
      <link>https://nvru.github.io/walkthrough/vulnhub/colddbox/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://nvru.github.io/walkthrough/vulnhub/colddbox/</guid>
      
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Attacker IP:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;10.245.58.142&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Target Machine IP:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;10.245.58.242&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The objective was to enumerate the target, gain initial access by compromising a vulnerable WordPress installation, and escalate privileges by abusing a misconfigured SUID binary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://nvru.github.io/images/vulnhub/colddbox/ss.png&#34; alt=&#34;Machine information&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;enumeration&#34;&gt;Enumeration&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;port-scanning&#34;&gt;Port Scanning&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;rustscan&#34;&gt;RustScan&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;rustscan -a 10.245.58.242
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Output:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-text&#34; data-lang=&#34;text&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Open 10.245.58.242:80
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Open 10.245.58.242:4512
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4 id=&#34;nmap&#34;&gt;Nmap&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo nmap -sSCV -A -p80,4512 -oN nmap/ports 10.245.58.242
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Results:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-text&#34; data-lang=&#34;text&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;PORT     STATE SERVICE VERSION
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;80/tcp   open  http    Apache httpd 2.4.18 (Ubuntu)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;4512/tcp open  ssh     OpenSSH 7.2p2 Ubuntu 4ubuntu2.10
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;HTTP Title: ColddBox | One more machine
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;WordPress 4.1.31
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Only two TCP ports were exposed: HTTP on port &lt;strong&gt;80&lt;/strong&gt; and SSH on port &lt;strong&gt;4512&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
